ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectOrder No. 165 - (Northwest Territories) Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 165 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the federal government to provide financial assistance to the NORTHWEST TERRITORIES with respect to the FLOODING AND MUDSLIDES causing damage to private property and provincial and municipal infrastructure in Nahanni Butte in early June 2012.
